      <div class="content-block__content">
        <p class="content-block__body-text">We are passionate about what we design, how we make it, and what happens to the things we put into the world.</p>

        <p>Because we are aware of the impact our furniture has on the planet, we make conscious decisions in every aspect of our design process about how to minimise the environmental impact of our furniture and extend its lifetime.</p>

        <p>We craft each piece with care and use responsibly sourced materials such as sustainably certified wood and recycled fabrics. Our furniture is customisable to suit the customers’ needs, and made-to-order to avoid excess stock. Our entire collection is produced in Europe, a great deal of it even in the Netherlands. To ensure our products never end up as waste, we offer various services including repairs, refurbishment, upgrades and returns.</p>
